                <head>Circus and Menagerie</head>
                <origin/>
                <commentary/>
                <transcript>
                    <p/>
                </transcript>
                <trailer/>
                <names/>
                <summary>John Robinson's Circus and Menagerie will perform in Chambersburg on August
                    18th. The circus will boast one of the largest collection of exotic animals ever
                    displayed in town. Acrobatic and equestrian performances along with a Female
                    Lion Enchantress should also draw large crowds.</summary>
