                <summary>The Chambersburg Cornet Band thanks the people of the borough for their
                    support. They also thank Prof. Shumaker for use of the Academy grounds and the
                    Misses Chambers for the use of the Rosedale Grounds. The band hopes to be a
                    source of entertainment, pleasure, and charity for some time to come.</summary>
